<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Wed, 29 Jun 2022 08:24:11 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>郭明錤：Apple 研發 5G 晶片失敗    iPhone 14,15 將沿用高通晶片</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/06/29/apple-iphone-5g/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=apple-iphone-5g</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 29 Jun 2022 08:24:11 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apple]]></category><category><![CDATA[iPhone]]></category><category><![CDATA[高通]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1107480</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>去年有傳 Apple 將會推出自家製 iPhone 5G 晶片，以取代現時使用的高通晶片。不過近日有指 App [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">去年有傳 Apple 將會推出自家製 iPhone 5G 晶片，以取代現時使用的高通晶片。不過近日有指 Apple 研發失敗，將會繼續沿用高通晶片，預計高通營收遠超市場預期。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">天風國際分析師郭明錤週二（28 日）在 Twitter 上稱有調查指，Apple 研發自家製 iPhone 5G 晶片失敗，因此將會沿用高通的 5G 晶片。預計高通會於 2023 年下半年與 2024 年上半年獨家向 Apple 供應 5G 晶片，使其營收及利潤或會遠超市場預期。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">(2/4)<br />My take:<br />1. Qualcomm&#39;s revenue and EPS in 2H23-1H24 will likely beat market consensus thanks to its sole supplier position for 5G chips of 2H23 new iPhones as Apple fails to replace Qualcomm.</p><p>&mdash; 郭明錤 (Ming-Chi Kuo) (@mingchikuo) <a href="https://twitter.com/mingchikuo/status/1541814296367484928?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">June 28, 2022</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">雖然現時 Apple 研發自家製 iPhone 5G 晶片失敗，但郭明錤推算 Apple 仍會繼續研發直至其推出的 5G 晶片能完全取代高通晶片。不過屆時高通業務或已發展成熟，即使失去 Apple 的晶片訂單，亦對高通業務的負面影響有限。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">(3/4)<br />2. I believe Apple will continue to develop its own 5G chips, but by the time Apple succeeds and can replace Qualcomm, Qualcomm&#39;s other new businesses should have grown enough to significantly offset the negative impacts caused by the order loss of iPhone 5G chips.</p><p>&mdash; 郭明錤 (Ming-Chi Kuo) (@mingchikuo) <a href="https://twitter.com/mingchikuo/status/1541814298510774273?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">June 28, 2022</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">早前有傳 Apple 會成功研發自家製 5G 晶片，將對高通晶片的依賴度下降。高通在去年預計，高通在 2023 年向 Apple 供應的晶片量會由 100% 遞減至 20 %。但現階段估計，Apple 至少仍會在未來兩年的 iPhone 中使用高通晶片。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.cnbc.com/2022/06/28/qualcomm-jumps-on-report-that-apples-2023-iphone-will-use-its-modems-.html">CNBC</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">—</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</u></a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
