</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>【報價】SONY INZONE H9/H7/H3 電競耳機，香港售價 + 詳細規格</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/06/29/sony-inzone-h9h7h3/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=sony-inzone-h9h7h3</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 29 Jun 2022 03:00:49 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[音樂耳機]]></category><category><![CDATA[INZONE]]></category><category><![CDATA[SONY]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1106748</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>香港 Sony 今日正式發佈 INZONE 電競耳機系列，系列有 3 款產品 INZONE H9、INZONE [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>香港 Sony 今日正式發佈 INZONE 電競耳機系列，系列有 3 款產品 INZONE H9、INZONE H7 以及 INZONE H3，專門為電競愛好者而設。無線版 H9、H7 耳機備有 USB 連接器與藍牙連接功能，連接電腦、遊戲機等以得到低延遲率的遊戲聽覺體驗，也可無線連接智能手機等。旗艦版本 INZONE H9 內置 ANC 主動降噪功能，讓玩家更專注於遊戲世界中。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/DSC09532 副本-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1107407 size-large" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/DSC09532 副本-902x900.jpg" alt="" width="902" height="900" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/DSC09532 副本-902x900.jpg 902w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/DSC09532 副本-581x580.jpg 581w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/DSC09532 副本-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/DSC09532 副本-768x766.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/DSC09532 副本-1536x1533.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/DSC09532 副本-2048x2044.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0014-5.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107380" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0014-5-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0014-5-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0014-5-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0014-5.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>SONY INZONE 電競耳機系列一口氣推出 3 款產品，包括：</p><p>INZONE H9：2.4GHz 與藍牙無線連接、3.5mm 耳機線連接、具備 ANC 主動降噪功能</p><p>INZONE H7：2.4GHz 與藍牙無線連接、3.5mm 耳機線連接</p><p>INZONE H3：3.5mm 耳機線連接</p><h2>INZONE H9 試用影片 :</h2><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_70691"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/mZ6df10EdiM?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0059-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107398" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0059-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0059-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0059-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0059-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲無線機種設 2.4GHz USB 連接器</p><h2>PS5 配色與質感、H9/H7/H3 各有分別</h2><p>三款產品都採用與 PlayStation 5 手掣極為相似的配色以及質感，摸上去不容易冼手。多種設計參考了 SONY 旗艦耳機 WH-1000XM5，例如耳機鉸位使用了特別組件更順滑調節耳機角度，還有 H9 耳機的耳墊使用了與 WH-1000XM5 相同的柔軟物料，戴上耳機後有同樣的舒適感覺（H7 與 H3 使用高柔軟性尼龍物料）。INZONE 全系列耳機都減低了側壓的力度，就算是佩戴眼鏡的朋友也可用得舒適。INZONE 定位在電競愛好者市場，無線版 INZONE H9、INZONE H7 附隨了 USB 2.4GHz 無線連接棒，另外耳機有語音通話專用咪高風。INZONE H7, H9 兩個無線型號在使用 2.4GHz 無線連接時，可調節遊戲音量與音訊聊天 voice chat 音量的平衡。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0041-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107401" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0041-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0041-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0041-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0041-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0023-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107382" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0023-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0023-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0023-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0023-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0025-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107381" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0025-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0025-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0025-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0025-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>旗艦機種 INZONE H9 備有 ANC 主動降噪功能。而且耳機上有發光的 LED 燈圈，發出微微藍光。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0034-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107383" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0034-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0034-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0034-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0034-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>作為電競機種，INZONE 3 款耳機都支援 360 Spatial Sound 空間定位音源，Sony 指其模擬頭外定位方式，玩家可聽到好像從四面八方而來，並且有距離感的音源，在 FPS/TPS 遊戲中可精準定位敵人位置甚至距離。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0079.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107395" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0079-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0079-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0079-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0079.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0080.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107396" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0080-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0080-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0080-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0080.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>配合電腦 INZONE HUB 應用程式模擬戰場定位</h2><p>在 PC 上，玩家可安裝 INZONE HUB 應用程式，配合手機應用程式「360 Spatial Sound Personalizer」把遊戲世界中的音源虛擬定位化，其個人化系統透過手機圖像拍攝用家的耳朵，從而提供更準確的定位音源輸出。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0047-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107384" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0047-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0047-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0047-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0047-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0056.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107386" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0056-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0056-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0056-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0056.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>電腦應用程式 INZONE HUB 可設定個人化音源定位，可設定 EQ 等化器，以及設定耳機的降噪功能開關。</p><p>硬件方面，耳機單元與外殼都特別為呈現不同頻率的音源，特別是震撼重低音而設計，提升遊戲中爆破聲音、槍聲的震撼力。</p><p>3 款耳機都備有 boom 咪高風貼近玩家的口部位置，同時旗艦款 H9 與高階款 H7 使用了雙向咪高風加上語音訊號處理系統，可除去玩家聲音以外的其他噪音。咪高風並有簡易靜音功能，只要用家把咪高風扭上，聽到「噠」一聲就代表咪高風靜音，在緊急需要靜音時，毋須東找西找其按鈕。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0094.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107387" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0094-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0094-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0094-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0094.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0078.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107394" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0078-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0078-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0078-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0078.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>在旗艦機 INZONE H9 會提供 ANC 主動降噪功能，透過「Dual Noise Sensor Technology」雙噪音感應技術與耳機上 4 個收音咪（左右耳機的向外收音咪各 1、左右耳機的內部收音咪各 1），把家居中經常聽到的冷氣機引擎聲、雪櫃聲、風扇噪音、地盤聲、電腦散熱扇聲音等都可以隔絕。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0032-4.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107403" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0032-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0032-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0032-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0032-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0028-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107404" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0028-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0028-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0028-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0028-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>INZONE H9 同時提供 Ambient Sound 環境音功能，用家可在耳機的物理按鈕上，快速切換 ANC 降噪開啟／AMB 環境音／降噪關閉。如希望在打機的同時隨時接收屋企人的聲音，就可開啟環境音功能。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0082.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107393" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0082-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0082-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0082-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0082.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>無線版耳機內置有長續航力電池，SONY 指耳機可連續播放音訊達 24 小時（ANC 主動降噪功能關閉時），而且耳機支援邊充電邊使用，玩家可連接附隨的 USB 線到電腦或充電器，並且一邊使用耳機。快速充電功能讓用家只充電 10 分鐘就能獲得 60 分鐘的續航力。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0090.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107391" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0090-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0090-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0090-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0090.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0067-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107397" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0067-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0067-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0067-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0067-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>發售日期及售價</h2><p>SONY INZONE 電競耳機系列將於 2022 年 7 月中旬發售，售價如下：</p><p>INZONE H9 無線電競降噪耳機　售價為港幣 2,590 元。<br />INZONE H7 無線電競耳機　售價為港幣 1,790 元。<br />INZONE H3 有線電競耳機　售價為港幣 799 元。</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id